---
title: "首页"
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="home-header">
  <h1>产品经理工作流</h1>
  <p>从发现问题到迭代优化的完整闭环，每个阶段配有可直接使用的 AI 技能。</p>
  <div class="meta">6 个阶段 · 40+ 技能 · 14 个工具</div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="phase-grid">
    {%- for p in phases %}
    <a href="/{{ p.id }}/" class="phase-card {{ p.id }}">
      <span class="card-icon">{{ p.emoji }}</span>
      <h2>{{ p.name }}</h2>
      <div class="question">{{ p.question }}</div>
      <div class="output">产出：{{ p.outputs | join(" · ") }}</div>
      <div class="card-skills-label">阶段技能</div>
      <div class="card-skills">
        {%- for s in p.skills %}
        <code>{{ s.cmd }} {{ s.title }}</code>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
    </a>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<div class="quick-start">
  <h2>快速上手</h2>
  <div class="quick-grid">
    <div class="quick-item">
      <code>/interview-synthesis</code>
      <span>日常需求评审，输入原始访谈记录</span>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-item">
      <code>/prd</code>
      <span>写 PRD，vibe coding 场景</span>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-item">
      <code>/vibe-prd-writer</code>
      <span>完整项目规范，直接喂给 Claude Code</span>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-item">
      <code>/meeting-to-action</code>
      <span>整理会议纪要，提取行动项</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
